---
import CornellNote from '../../../components/CornellNote.astro';
---

<html lang="ko">
	<head>
		<meta charset="utf-8" />
		<link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="/favicon.svg" />
		<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width" />
		<title>유형 07 - 난이도 [하] 연습</title>
		<!-- KaTeX -->
		<link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/katex@0.16.11/dist/katex.min.css">
		<script is:inline src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/katex@0.16.11/dist/katex.min.js"></script>
		<script is:inline src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/katex@0.16.11/dist/contrib/auto-render.min.js"></script>
		<style>
			body {
				background-color: #e0e0e0;
				margin: 0;
				padding: 20px;
				display: flex;
				justify-content: center;
			}
			.sol-button {
				display: inline-block;
				padding: 4px 12px;
				background: #eef2f8;
				color: #1a73e8;
				border-radius: 8px;
				text-decoration: none;
				font-size: 0.9rem;
				font-weight: bold;
				margin-left: 10px;
				border: 1.5px solid #d0e0f0;
				transition: all 0.2s ease;
			}
			.sol-button:hover {
				background: #1a73e8;
				color: white;
				transform: translateY(-1px);
				box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(26, 115, 232, 0.2);
			}
			.question-card {
				background: white;
				padding: 20px;
				border-radius: 12px;
				margin-bottom: 20px;
				border: 1px solid #eee;
			}
			.question-header {
				display: flex;
				justify-content: space-between;
				align-items: center;
				margin-bottom: 15px;
			}
		</style>
	</head>
	<body>
		<CornellNote title="유형 07. [하] 기초 탄탄" chapter="Level: Low">
			<div slot="cues">
				<p style="margin: 0; font-weight: bold; color: #1a1a1a;">🟢 기초 포인트</p>
				<ul style="margin-top: 10px; padding-left: 18px; font-size: 11pt; line-height: 1.6; color: #444;">
					<li>분모가 0이 되는 지점 확인</li>
					<li>단순 미정계수 1개 풀이</li>
					<li>함숫값과 좌우극한 일치</li>
				</ul>
			</div>

			<section>
				<div class="type-section">
					<p style="margin-bottom: 20px;">한 점에서의 연속 개념을 기초 문제를 통해 익힙니다.</p>
					
					<!-- Q1 -->
					<div class="question-card">
						<div class="question-header">
							<p style="margin: 0;"><b>Q1.</b> 함수 { "$ f(x) = \\begin{cases} \\frac{x^2-1}{x-1} & (x \\neq 1) \\\\ k & (x=1) \\end{cases} $" } 이 $x=1$에서 연속일 때, $k$의 값은?</p>
							<a href="/wiki/chapter01/solutions/type07-low/q1" class="sol-button">풀이 💡</a>
						</div>
					</div>

					<!-- Q2 -->
					<div class="question-card">
						<div class="question-header">
							<p style="margin: 0;"><b>Q2.</b> 함수 { "$ f(x) = \\begin{cases} \\frac{x+a}{x+3} & (x \\neq -3) \\\\ 2 & (x=-3) \\end{cases} $" } 이 $x=-3$에서 연속일 때, $a$의 값은?</p>
							<span class="sol-button" style="background: #eee; color: #999; border-color: #ddd; cursor: not-allowed;">준비 중</span>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>

				<!-- Navigation -->
				<div style="margin-top: 40px; display: flex; gap: 20px; align-items: center; justify-content: center;">
					<a href="/wiki/chapter01/types/type07/" style="color: #666; text-decoration: none; font-size: 10pt; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 5px;">
						<span style="font-size: 12pt;">←</span> 핵심 문제로 이동
					</a>
					<div style="width: 1px; height: 12px; background: #ddd;"></div>
					<a href="/wiki/chapter01/problems-cont/" style="color: #666; text-decoration: none; font-size: 10pt;">
						목록으로 돌아가기
					</a>
				</div>
			</section>
		</CornellNote>

		<script is:inline>
			if (typeof window !== 'undefined') {
				document.addEventListener("DOMContentLoaded", function() {
					if (typeof renderMathInElement === 'function') {
						renderMathInElement(document.body, {
							delimiters: [
								{left: '$$', right: '$$', display: true},
								{left: '$', right: '$', display: false}
							],
							throwOnError : false
						});
					}
				});
			}
		</script>
	</body>
</html>
